ssh: command line interface utility for mac or linux + windows>=10
for windows<10 + >=10, use putty
for everything, ec2 instance connect.

i for identity file with extension pem
protect the pem file for future errors: for windows, change the users.
commands to connect to an ec2 instance using ssh:

ssh
ssh -i path ec2-user@ipv4publicip


connect to an ec2 instance using ec2 instance connect

provide aws credentials to our ec2 instance; through iam roles and not aws configure.


